description:
*The Joker Movie: The Most Triggering Movie of 2019* | Despite the negative criticism circulating the media, the 2019 Joker film still topped the charts at over $1 billion, making it the highest-grossing horror movie of all time. A lot was said about the film, from its glorification of violence to its portrayal of mental health. In this episode of LED Live, we explore the impact this film has on society and how it could be impacting you... @dcofficial
